title: ISic000192. I.Sicily inscription 000192
body:
Facsimile Images

ex ((·)) d(ecreto) ((·)) d(ecurionum)
l(ocus) ((·)) p(ublice) ((·)) d(atus) P(ublio) Lo[---]
XXXV

Apparatus criticus

Text of autopsy

translation

commentary

Bivona (1994) hypothetically suggests that the missing name, in the dative case, at the end of line to, is a member of the gens Lollia, known elsewhere in Termini, see ISic000058.
